{"abstract": "A new book by Kenneth Feinberg traces his years of work in assessing and paying victims\u2019 claims after disasters, whether the 9/11 attacks, the Virginia Tech massacre or the Gulf of Mexico oil spill.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2012/08/05/business/kenneth-feinbergs-new-look-at-fairnesss-price-review.html", "snippet": "A new book by Kenneth Feinberg traces his years of work in assessing and paying victims\u2019 claims after disasters, whether the 9/11 attacks, the Virginia Tech massacre or the Gulf of Mexico oil spill.", "lead_paragraph": "KENNETH R. FEINBERG, who styles himself as \u201ca lawyer and mediator in one,\u201d has made a career of handling hot potatoes and moving them from politicians\u2019 plates to his own. At moments of national disaster, he has embraced the trying task of applying mere money to sustain and comfort the survivors and to bind the wounds of the afflicted. ", "print_section": "BU", "print_page": "5", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2012/08/05/business/05SHELF/05SHELF-jumbo.jpg", "height": 1024, "width": 646, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2012/08/05/business/05SHELF/05SHELF-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 2048, "width": 1291, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2012/08/05/business/05SHELF/05SHELF-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2012/08/05/business/05SHELF/05SHELF-thumbStandard.jpg", "thumbnailwidth": 75, "thumbnailheight": 75}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbLarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2012/08/05/business/05S